objects.name: survey
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE survey (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	mturk_id VARCHAR(20), 
	type VARCHAR(20), 
	data JSON, 
	timestamp DATETIME, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(mturk_id) REFERENCES user (mturk_id)
)

objects.name: task
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE task (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	mturk_id VARCHAR(20), 
	task_type VARCHAR(50), 
	task_instance INTEGER, 
	data JSON, 
	score INTEGER, 
	completed BOOLEAN, 
	timestamp DATETIME, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(mturk_id) REFERENCES user (mturk_id)
)

objects.name: task_completion
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE task_completion (
	id INTEGER NOT NULL, 
	user_id VARCHAR(64), 
	task_type VARCHAR(50), 
	completed BOOLEAN, 
	PRIMARY KEY (id), 
	FOREIGN KEY(user_id) REFERENCES user (mturk_id)
)

objects.name: user
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE user (
	mturk_id VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL, 
	experiment_completed BOOLEAN, 
	intervention_condition INTEGER, 
	PRIMARY KEY (mturk_id), 
	UNIQUE (mturk_id)
)
